These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, kale, grapefruit, mango
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
2. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person eating mango##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating grapefruit is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person eating mango is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Food   | mango | raspberry     | grapefruit | kale |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, rock, techno
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, action, zombie, superhero
1. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of techno is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
5. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop    | techno     | rock  |
| Movie-Genre     | horror    | zombie | action | superhero |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, pineapple, carrot
4 different pets are kept: cat, lizard, rabbit, snake
1. the owner of the snake is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
2. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
5. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating pineapple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Food   | lime   | pineapple   | corn  | carrot |
| Pet           | lizard | snake | rabbit | cat  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, family, spy, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
2. the person watching epic movies is between the person watching animation movies and the egyptian##2
3. the person watching epic movies is on the left or right of the person watching spy movies##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre         | family | animation | epic | spy  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

