The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, train, tram
1. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the tram and the person who growsorchid##2
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person who growspoppy##2
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Flower    | poppy | orchid | aconite | daisy |
| Transport   | roller | boat  | train    | tram  |

