.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, filmmaking, fishing
House: wooden, modern, townhouse, tower
1. the wooden house is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the modern house##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the townhouse house##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
5. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
6. the modern house is on the left or right of the townhouse house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | fishing | filmmaking | board-games | drawing   |
| House   | modern | townhouse | wooden      | tower |

