.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, december, july, november
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, skiing, tennis, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday     | october | december   | july      | november      |
| Sport   | skiing     | tennis | basketball | volleyball |

