4. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
5. the person driving the tram is on the left or right of the tower house##3
6. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| House       | tower | cape-cod | futuristic    | palace      |
| Transport   | taxi       | tram       | snowmobile | skateboard |

