.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-14::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, cabbage, plum, potato
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, havana, ritmeester, pall-mall
1. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the havana-smoker##3
2. the havana-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the game-smoker##1
4. the havana-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating plum is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | cabbage  | artichoke | potato  | plum      |
| Cigar    | pall-mall | game | ritmeester | havana |

