The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, indie, punk
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
3. the person traveling to rome is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| City      | rome | marseilles    | liverpool  | edinburgh |
| Music-Genre   | disco       | dubstep | indie | punk  |

