4. the person watching spy movies is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growssunflower is between the person watching spy movies and the person who growsbellflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |  4  |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | horror  | animation  | spy |
| Flower           | lily    | bellflower | sunflower | zinnia |

